caption:
それぞれの主観の中でのいい人例えば…

立派な人

華やかな人

やさしい人

世界の信念を反映するどんな素晴らしい人よりも

わたしは

差し出されたしごとを

ことばにはできない世界のことの方が

圧倒的に大きいのだということに

気づかされるから

summary: What I’ll be doing for now on.
title: What I’ll be doing for now on.
body:
So, I’m just going to do a quick summary of what happened in May. Similar to April when I had a lot of personal problems, but family related issues came up and I had to take care and make sure my family are alright and doing well. So I hadn’t really been active nor posting much this month, except, for working on my comic. On my family’s end: They’re doing all better, which I’m thankful for.

I had came to the conclusion that I’ll be working on my comic mostly for now on based upon what happened. What I will do - despite what I said back in April WIPs - is show sneak WIP peeks of my comic pages. If it’s a single panel WIP it’ll be posted publicly (free to view), but if it’s a whole page WIP then it’s only for patrons only.

Be aware that there will be a large watermark over it for protection since it’s still in the making. To show that I am still active as an artist & creator and to let you guys know I am indeed serious about my comic and sharing it’s story with you guys.

On the side with my comic, I’ll slowly be working on my illustrations. Such as “At the Bar” and a few other things, but those will be slower in progress compared to the comic pages. I’ll be posting those on my YouTube as speedpaints nor art talks to keep my YouTube channel going.

Thank you for you patience and understanding.
